Bring The Playground Home. Don’T Let Weather Dictate When Your Kids Can Go To The Park To Run Around. Rain Or Shine, This Indoor Slide Is Ready To Deliver Hours Of Fun At The Snap Of A Finger!
Our Patented Strongfold Cardboard Supports Up To 50 Lbs And Is Super Durable And Safe (Push In The Side Flaps For Added Reinforcement). It’S Also 100% Recyclable When You’Re Done With It. Product Size: 59”L X 25”W X 28”D. Ages 2-5.
Spacesaver. Tired Of Toys Piling Up? Say Goodbye To Messy Playrooms & Crowded Living Rooms. Pop2Play, Then Pop It Away. Folds Flat So You Can Easily Put It Away When You’Re Done. Scan The Qr Code On The Left To See How It Looks And Fits In Your Home!
Pop Up The Fun! Instantly Turn Any Room Into A Play Area! Lightweight And Portable, Take This Toddler Slide With You Wherever You Go And Keep Your Young Ones Entertained For Hours. Who Said Playing Indoors Is Boring?!
EASY ASSEMBLY, EASIER CLEAN-UP. Most playsets take time to put together, are difficult to store and expensive to buy. Not this one! Pop2Play’s budget-friendly foldaway kids slide assembles in a snap and is just as easy to wipe clean!

Award Winning Magic Touch technology – All the durability and keepsake value of a classic wooden toy, elevated with today’s latest technology. Even the gentlest tap on the painted piano keys makes real piano sounds.
10 popular melodies – Baby can choose from 10 songs on 5 music cards and follow the color dots to master each tune. Features family favorites like "Baa, Baa, Black Sheep" and “Wheels on the Bus.” Off/Low/High volume control will please baby’s biggest fans (Mom & Dad).
Safe & easy-to-clean design – Together in Tune instruments connect simply, safely, and wirelessly via radio signals. Buttonless wooden design makes the piano extra easy to wipe clean. Appropriate for children ages 12 months and up.
